No. 11-6974. Eleutorio Cortijo, Petitioner v. Steven Racette, Superintendent, Elmira Correctional Facility, et al. 565 U.S. 1073, 132 S. Ct. 786,

181 L. Ed. 2d 509,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8389. November 28, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.

Justice Sotomayor took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 422 Fed. Appx. 12.
